---
title: "darksouls3:No-Logo Mod"
---

The **No-Logo mod** is a (allowed for speedrunning) modification for **[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii)** that completely removes the intro logo screens from the game. These are the logos normally shown when first starting DS3 and after saving and quitting the game, every time.\
The mod was created by **[blcd](//github.com/bladecoding/DarkSouls3RemoveIntroScreens),** works on **v1.04** and various patches from **v1.08** up to the **Current Patch** of **[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii)**.

